---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Speaking">
  <div class="speaking-page">
    <header class="speaking-header">
      <h1>Speaking</h1>
      <p>I speak about spatial cognition, AI alignment, relational knowledge systems, and the future of learning.</p>
    </header>
    
    <section class="bio-section">
      <h2>Bio</h2>
      
      <div class="bio-version">
        <h3>Short (50 words)</h3>
        <p>Sam Mathews Chase is the founder of LOCI, a spatial training company using method of loci techniques for industrial safety. With a background in neuroscience and electronic music (as Blondtron), Sam explores how relational thinking can reshape AI, learning, and human connection.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bio-version">
        <h3>Medium (100 words)</h3>
        <p>Sam Mathews Chase is the founder of LOCI, a safety training company that uses spatial cognition and method of loci techniques to create interactive, location-based learning experiences for the mining industry. Collaborating with research institutions including UCL's Human Memory and Navigation Lab, Sam bridges fundamental neuroscience research into practical systems that have reached millions of users. As an electronic musician performing as Blondtron, Sam brings a creative lens to questions about consciousness, AI alignment, and how relational knowledge systems might offer alternatives to current approaches in machine learning.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
    
<section class="headshots-section">
  <h2>Headshots</h2>
  <div class="headshots-grid">
    <a href="/images/headshots/Sam full square.jpg" download>
      <img src="/images/headshots/Sam full square.jpg" alt="Sam - Square" />
    </a>
    <a href="/images/headshots/Sam full.jpg" download>
      <img src="/images/headshots/Sam full.jpg" alt="Sam - Full" />
    </a>
    <a href="/images/headshots/Sam Headshot Smiling.jpg" download>
      <img src="/images/headshots/Sam Headshot Smiling.jpg" alt="Sam - Smiling" />
    </a>
  </div>
  <p class="download-note">Click to download</p>
</section>
    
    <section class="topics-section">
      <h2>Topics & Expertise</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Spatial Cognition & Learning</strong> — Method of loci, memory palaces, location-based training</li>
        <li><strong>AI & Relational Knowledge</strong> — What gets dropped in compression, animate grammar for AI</li>
        <li><strong>The Five Hundred Year Rule</strong> — Why institutions, populations, and AI models collapse in similar ways</li>
        <li><strong>XR & Immersive Experiences</strong> — WebXR, VR training, interactive installations</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    
    <section class="contact-section">
      <h2>Book Me</h2>
      <p>For speaking inquiries, reach out at <a href="mailto:sam@loci.ca">sam@loci.ca</a></p>
    </section>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .speaking-page {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
  }
  
  .speaking-header {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }
  
  .speaking-header h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .speaking-header p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--sand);
  }
  
  section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  
  h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--wood);
  }
  
  .bio-version {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--night);
    border: 1px solid var(--wood);
    border-radius: 6px;
  }
  
  .bio-version h3 {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--stone);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  
  .bio-version p {
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  
  .placeholder {
    color: var(--stone);
    font-style: italic;
  }
  
  .topics-section ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }
  
  .topics-section li {
    padding: 1rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--wood);
  }
  
  .contact-section a {
    color: var(--ember);
  }
  .headshots-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 1rem;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.headshots-grid a {
  border-radius: 6px;
  overflow: hidden;
  border: 1px solid var(--wood);
  transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
}

.headshots-grid a:hover {
  border-color: var(--ember);
}

.headshots-grid img {
  width: 100%;
  height: auto;
  display: block;
}

.download-note {
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  color: var(--stone);
  font-style: italic;
}
</style>